txt.en:
SUMMONS: IMMEDIATE EVACUATION TO FORLAW

The Reeve summons all people of Wildermore to evacuate to Forlaw at once. You are in danger. The forces of Isengard storm the land, and a fell winter is upon us. You are no longer safe; make haste, and beware of the armies of Isengard, and of winter storms.

Gárwig
Thane of Forlaw, Reeve of Wildermore
